means_churn = []
n = 1
while n < 500:
    n += 1
    sample = data_product[data_product['churn'] == 1].sample(1000)['age'].mean()
    means_churn.append(sample)

alpha = 0.05   

results = st.shapiro(means_churn)

print('p-:', results.pvalue)

if results.pvalue < alpha:
    print('  ')
else:
    print('    ')
